For all of you football manager folks, this soccer manager game will be extremely fun. Top Eleven 2022 is an award winning mobile soccer manager game and it will put you in charge of your very own soccer club. In this game you can give your tactics a specialized touch by developing various playing styles of your players. There is a feature that allows you a deeper level of control over how the players play each match in the game. What is more, you can assign variou skill-sets that correspond to the skills of your favorite soccer legends. 

Top Eleven 2022 is a complete soccer competition and univers on your phone and it allows you to compete with other managers from around the world. The game is a real-time soccer management game and it is ready for you to show off your management skills. You can also get some advice in the game from various players and coaches in order to improve your own management skills in the game. You can also develop and set formations that can deliver wins in your daily games and you can manage your time in real-time PVP fixtures.
